Remillard spectral state definitions, and we find that these definitions alone do not provide a complete description of the outburst. Finally, for several of the observations, the high-energy emission is dominated by the nearby sources IGR J16320–4751 and IGR J16358–4726, and we provide information on when these sources were bright and on the nature of their energy spectra. Subject},
